    "description": "Pole To Win Holdings, Inc., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the testing/verification and evaluation, and Internet supporting businesses in Japan and internationally. The company offers testing, customer support, localization, and support for overseas expansion services for gaming market; software testing, infrastructure setup, server monitoring, data center operations, and kitting services for tech market; and monitoring and customer support services for e-commerce market. It also provides app development and website management, crowdfunding operation, barrier-free subtitles and audio guides, barrier-free consulting, testing and localization, voice recording at house studio, art production, game development support, and customer support for game users. The company was formerly known as Poletowin Pitcrew Holdings, Inc. and changed its name to Pole To Win Holdings, Inc. in May 2022. Pole To Win Holdings, Inc. was incorporated in 2009 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
